summary: An ordinance relating to the Water Dept. and authorizing the sale and removal of certain second growth timber and salvageable forest materials from city owned lands in Townships 22 & 23 North, Range 7 East, Townships 21, 22 & 23 North, Range 8 East, and Township 22 North, Range 9 East, W.M., in the Cedar River Watershed under contract with the Scott Paper Company during 1961-62.
